    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! You honestly won't believe the condition of this beauty. It\u2019s been my absolute pride and joy, and I\u2019ve taken such good care of it that it still looks and smells like it just rolled off the showroom floor! There isn't a single scratch or dent to be found, and it drives like an absolute dream. If you\u2019re looking for a ride that\u2019s basically perfect without the brand-new price tag, this is definitely the one for you. I'd love to see it go to someone who will appreciate it as much as I have\u2014feel free to reach out with any questions!",
