      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "This 2018 Porsche 718 Cayman is a true collector\u2019s specimen, presented in showroom condition. Every inch of the vibrant Miami Blue exterior has been protected with a professional multi-layer ceramic coating, ensuring a mirror-like finish completely free of stone chips, swirls, or imperfections. Inside, the cabin is immaculate; the black leather remains supple and taut with zero bolster wear, and the controls still retain their factory-crisp tactile feel. Mechanically, the car is beyond reproach, having been exclusively maintained at authorized Porsche centers with a full, documented service history included. Always garage-kept under a climate-controlled cover and never exposed to rain or snow, this vehicle looks and drives as if it just rolled off the assembly line. It is a turn-key masterpiece for the most discerning enthusiast.",
      "price": 48500.0,
