      "description": "Hey there! \ud83d\udc4b Are you looking for a ride that looks and feels like it just rolled off the showroom floor? This beauty is in absolute mint condition and has been pampered like a member of the family! It\u2019s seriously flawless inside and out\u2014no scratches, no spills, just pure driving perfection. I\u2019m honestly sad to see it go, but I know it\u2019s going to make its next owner so happy. Come take a look and see for yourself; it\u2019s even better in person! \u2728",
